b|url=https://fanprojplay.net/tv-show/ubax/?series=ubax|title=Ubax Television Show|lang=so}}</ref>\n| June 21, 2019\n| 20:00\n| TBA\n|-\n| {{SRB}}\n| [[Pink TV (Serbia)|Pink TV]]\n|  ''\u041d\u0435\u043c\u043e\u0433\u0443\u045b\u0430 \u0459\u0443\u0431\u0430\u0432''<br/><small>''Nemogu\u0107a ljubav''</small>\n| December 23, 2019\n| 20:00\n| TBA\n|-\n| {{UZB}}\n| [[Sevimli TV(UZBEKISTAN)|Sevimli TV]]\n|  ''Beqaror''\n| August 8, 2019\n| 20:30\n| TBA\n|-\n| {{CHL}}\n| [[Televisi\u00f3n Nacional de Chile|TVN]]\n| Hercai\n| December 8, 2019\n| Sunday to Thursday 22:40-23:40\n| TBA\n|-\n| {{ESP}}\n| Nova\n|  \n| 2019\n| \n| TBA\n|-\n| {{CRO}}\n| [[Nova TV (Croatia)|Nova TV]]\n|  ''Ljubav osvetnika''\n| January 6, 2020\n| 18:20\n| TBA\n|-\n| {{UKR}}\n|[[1+1 (TV channel)|1+1]]\n|'''\u0412\u0456\u0442\u0440\u044f\u043d\u0435 \u043a\u043e\u0445\u0430\u043d\u043d\u044f'''\n| April 3, 2020\n| 20:30\n|TBA\n|-\n|  {{UAE}}\n|| [[Dubai Tv]]\n|\u201c\u0632\u0647\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u062b\u0627\u0644\u0648\u062b\u201d\n| March 10, 2020\n| 12:00, 20:00\n|TBA\n|}\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\nhttps://tv.ua/tv/anonsy-na-tv/1214167-na-1-plus-1-sostoitsya-premera-novogo-turetskogo-seriala-vetrenaya-lyubov\n\n== External links ==\n* {{Official website|https://www.atv.com.tr/diziler/hercai/hakkinda}} {{in lang|tr}}\n* {{IMDb title|tt9721776}}\n\n[[Category:2019 Turkish television series debuts]]\n[[Category:Turkish drama television series]]\n[[Category:Turkish romance television series]]\n[[Category:2010s Turkish television series]]\n[[Category:ATV (Turkey) shows]]\n[[Category:Turkish-language television programs]]\n[[Category:Television shows set in Istanbul]]\n\n{{Turkey-tv-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Hercai ukraina", "label": "safe", "comment": "new", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hercai"}
{"title_page": "Jesse Kaislavuo", "text_new": "{{short description|Finnish cyclist}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2020}}\n{{Infobox cyclist\n| name           = Jesse Kaislavuo\n| image          = \n| caption        = \n| fullname       = \n| birth_date     = {{birth date and age|1992|4|24|df=yes}}\n| birth_place    = \n| death_date     = \n| death_place    = \n| height         = \n| weight         = \n| currentteam    = \n| discipline     = \n| role           = Rider\n| ridertype      = \n| amateuryears1  = \n| amateurteam1   = \n| proyears1      = \n| proteam1       = \n| majorwins      = \n| medaltemplates = \n| show-medals    = \n| updated        = \n}}\n'''Jesse Kaislavuo''' (born 24 April 1992) is a Finnish [[bicycle racing|racing cyclist]]. He won the [[Finnish National Road Race Championships|Finnish national road race title]] in 2016.<ref name=\"CyclingArchives\">{{cite web |url=http://www.cyclingarchives.com/ritfiche.php?ritid=278639 |title=National Championship, Road, Elite, Finland 2016 |accessdate=3 July 2016 |work=Cycling Archives}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{cycling archives|101415}}\n*{{ProCyclingStats|186531}}\n\n{{Finnish National Road Race Championships (men) |state=collapsed}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Kaislavuo, Jesse}}\n[[Category:1992 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Finnish male cyclists]]\n[[Category:Place of birth missing (living people)]]\n{{Finland-cycling-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Finnish cyclist}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=July 2016}}\n{{Infobox cyclist\n| name           = Jesse Kaislavuo\n| image          = \n| caption        = \n| fullname       = \n| birth_date     = {{birth date and age|1992|4|24|df=yes}}\n| birth_place    = \n| death_date     = \n| death_place    = \n| height         = \n| weight         = \n| currentteam    = \n| discipline     = \n| role           = Rider\n| ridertype      = \n| amateuryears1  = \n| amateurteam1   = \n| proyears1   